---
title: Salata (Tomato and Cucumber Salad)
layout: page
categories:
- sauces/toppings
region: Mediterranean
---
halve @cherry tomatoes{5%ounces} and dice @long english cucumber{1%half}.

Add veggies to a #sealable container{} (your going to be shaking it). Season with @red wine vinegar{1%tablespoon}, @olive oil{1%tablespoon}, @salt{1%teaspoon}, and @pepper{1/2%teaspoon}. Seal the container and shake well to mix.

Chill and serve. 
